fields.value: The app gives your shop a platform to show offers to the users, To increase your sales. For showing offers to the users you need to register. You can add offers without register, but to make the offer visible to the users, you need to register.

fields.message: Shop owners can now post offers to attract nearby customers to their shop
Posting Offers is very easy .Just register your shop and make your own brand.
Customers can now discover offers from nearby shops
